{"tid":1297192,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿拿奧杜域投上港 被鎚迷咒斷腳","createTime":"2019-07-08T14:48:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T14:56:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"03a285debf24529f59b77ca21ebfba2bf7abeef4","tid":1297192,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:48:59.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】上海上港周一宣佈從韋斯咸羅致前鋒阿拿奧杜域，被鎚迷在網上肆無忌憚地攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然兩家球會都沒有公佈，但據知阿拿奧杜域（Marko Arnautovic）的轉會費為2300萬鎊，而且周薪高達23萬鎊。這名30歲奧地利國腳將快盡快飛到上海，有機會趕及於7月13日作客江蘇蘇寧的中超上陣。<br />\n<br />\nArnie在1月已獲得中超球會青睞，他曾逼使韋斯咸放人不果後，180度U-turn續下新合約，但如今仍然離隊。<br />\n<br />\n鎚仔幫球迷向來愛恨分明，在阿拿奧杜域落實轉會後，紛紛於twitter表達憤怒之情。<br />\n<br />\n有人說：「拜拜X頭。我希望他在地標戰斷雙腳。」亦有人說：「慶幸他走了，我不能再忍受球會有這種愚蠢行為。」更有人說：「他無腰骨怎麼樣能夠通過體測？」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"8256c9ab2114bd9628de56b49d4e116d3cd18722","tid":1297192,"uid":43557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"最尾果句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf4b6fb988c02e0c4224221660af954dab90f1c","tid":1297192,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔係去國米咩"},{"pid":"e0b7d6c7ef95e127940c24e593968a813ba5bf7c","tid":1297192,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cf4b6fb988c02e0c4224221660af954dab90f1c","tid":1297192,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔係去國米咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"Marko Arnautovic departs West Ham United for Chinese Super League<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.whufc.com/news/articles/2019/july/08-july/marko-arnautovic-departs-west-ham-united-chinese-super-league\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whufc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019%2Fjuly%2F08-july%2Fmarko-arnautovic-departs-west-ham-united-chinese-super-league&d=QWAfKg5qpFwl